snippet.title: BomberCin 2 (2021 Demo Gameplay)
snippet.description:
After nearly 7 years of wait, BomberCin 2 has finally received a new update, with a massive load of new additions!
What's new?
A new reimagined bonus game, new graphics, new stages, a new type of enemy, completely original music and sound effects!

※ Download Link: https://kousaku-p.itch.io/bombercin2
